{"tid":323732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"相愛可惜屋企有件","createTime":"2017-07-15T22:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T02:22:55.000Z","uid":116390,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"400b8ff7f1edce01de52beb98a531c128633206f","tid":323732,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T22:31:41.000Z","msg":"我愛佢佢更愛我<br />\n可惜我屋企已經有個<br />\n雖然已經冇晒感情<br />\n但係責任問題局住過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb999f20a6dd667d8b8728a32582b78954609f5","tid":323732,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T23:06:17.000Z","msg":"我都有咁嘅經驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n度過了浪漫片段　回到了平凡家園<br />\n無奈地重頭打算<br />\n盡了責任你身邊　卻想她再見一面<br />\n心思一轉難復原<br />\n<br />\n日以繼夜學冷靜　何以卻仍然失眠<br />\n其實願從來不變<br />\n但妳永未像她般　瞭解到我每一面<br />\n甘心依靠我身邊<br />\n<br />\n又再抱緊這段緣　不想失去那一邊<br />\n唯盼望她跟妳終不遇見<br />\n<br />\n真正愛情　只差一線　非自願欺騙<br />\n不要說穿　小心打算　總會有彎轉<br />\n當錯鑄成　解釋只怕　傷害極深遠<br />\n給你開心　給她溫暖<br />\n不能言　是這地下情<br />\n<br />\n將最好的　給她給你<br />\n三人情　問怎麼共存"},{"pid":"97c55ba17ed98bc64fce2f144e5d4724333d01fa","tid":323732,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T23:09:40.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點先有勇氣/合適時機講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2908fdf03d89105faf0442b8a12b0cda59d7e0f3","tid":323732,"uid":56720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85e819f7ff02e489e0cdb88f06a9be5b90d1c0a3","tid":323732,"uid":23973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:50:47.000Z","msg":"嘩好可憐呀你屌你老母"},{"pid":"b1568f4925deb299669022a90c8ac62d0ebaa83f","tid":323732,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"自己做錯仲要扮受害者"},{"pid":"253b52e81760cee91aa4365522aae44908fa901b","tid":323732,"uid":53947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"